## install module locally 
ref: https://sites.google.com/a/case.edu/hpcc/hpc-cluster/software/software-installation-guide/perl-and-modules?pli=1

```
perl -MCPAN -e shell 

cpan> o conf makepl_arg 'PREFIX=~/perl5'
    makepl_arg         [PREFIX=~/perl5]
Please use 'o conf commit' to make the config permanent!
cpan> o conf commit
commit: wrote '/home/hxk728/.cpan/CPAN/MyConfig.pm'
```
